        <mxCell id="p6-title" value="里程碑与出门条件：通过的是质量门禁，不是扩大能力声明" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=26;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#111827;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#020617;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="30" width="1520" height="80" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-m" value="里程碑&#xa;M30.0 文档/边界冻结&#xa;M30.1 8 actions storyboard accepted&#xa;M30.2 8-action semantic candidate exists&#xa;M30.3 Motion QA rejects transform-only and accepts semantic candidate&#xa;M30.4 old-vs-new preview embeds visual evidence&#xa;M30.5 approved target-only apply and rollback pass&#xa;M30.6 final dashboard and scans close scoped passed" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=18;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=18;fillColor=#eff6ff;strokeColor=#3b82f6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="70" y="150" width="470" height="380" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-exit" value="出门条件&#xa;• V30.0-V30.5 evidence 存在并对应 PRD 阶段&#xa;• 至少一个 tested local 8-action pack 完成 storyboard / QA / preview / apply / rollback&#xa;• 弱动作仍被拒绝&#xa;• QA failed pack 不可应用&#xa;• target apply 只影响目标 PetInstance&#xa;• rollback 恢复 previous visible pack&#xa;• final evidence 是视觉嵌入，不是纯文本或链接&#xa;• security scan 和 claim scan clean" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=18;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=18;fillColor=#ecfdf5;strokeColor=#10b981;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="565" y="150" width="470" height="460" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-claim" value="最终允许声明&#xa;V30 semantic 2D pet animation quality passed for tested local action packs with storyboard, motion-readability QA, preview, target apply, and rollback evidence.&#xa;&#xa;审查重点&#xa;如果图或文档暗示任意猫、provider、Petdex、3D、发布或平台 ready，即为过度承诺。" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=18;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=18;fillColor=#fffbeb;strokeColor=#f59e0b;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="150" width="470" height="460" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
